geria's goal tally first.''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dzfoot.com/iframe_include/joueur_iframe.php?id=2100 |title=La fiche de Riyad Mahrez |publisher=DZFoot |accessdate=9 May 2015}}</ref>\n\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!No.!!Date!!Venue!!Opponent!!Score!!Result!!Competition\n|-\n| align=center | 1 || 15 October 2014 || rowspan=2 | [[Mustapha Tchaker Stadium]], [[Blida]], Algeria || {{fb|MWI}} || align=center | '''2'''\u20130 || align=center | 3\u20130 || rowspan=2|[[2015 Africa Cup of Nations qualification]]\n|-\n| align=center | 2 || 15 November 2014 || {{fb|ETH}} || align=center | '''2'''\u20131 || align=center | 3\u20131\n|-\n| align=center | 3 || 27 January 2015 || [[Nuevo Estadio de Malabo|Nuevo Estadio]], [[Malabo]], Equatorial Guinea || {{fb|SEN}} || align=center | '''1'''\u20130 || align=center | 2\u20130|| [[2015 Africa Cup of Nations]]\n|-\n| align=center | 4 || 17 November 2015 || rowspan=3 | Mustapha Tchaker Stadium, Blida, Algeria || {{fb|TAN}} || align=center | '''3'''\u20130 || align=center | 7\u20130 || [[2018 FIFA World Cup qualification (CAF)|2018 FIFA World Cup qualification]]\n|-\n| align=center | 5 || rowspan=2 | 4 September 2016 || rowspan=2 | {{fb|LES}} || align=center | '''2'''\u20130 || rowspan=2 align=center | 6\u20130 || rowspan=2 | [[2017 Africa Cup of Nations qualification]]\n|-\n| align=center | 6 || align=center | '''6'''\u20130\n|-\n| align=center | 7 || rowspan=2 | 15 January 2017 || rowspan=2 | [[Stade de Franceville]], [[Franceville]], Gabon || rowspan=2 | {{fb|ZIM}} || align=center | '''1'''\u20130 || rowspan=2 align=center | 2\u20132 || rowspan=2 | [[2017 Africa Cup of Nations]]\n|-\n| align=center | 8 || align=center | '''2'''\u20132\n|-\n| align=center | 9 || rowspan=2 | 18 November 2018 || rowspan=2 | [[Stade Municipal (Lom\u00e9)|Stade Municipal]], [[Lom\u00e9]], Togo || rowspan=2 | {{fb|TOG}} || align=center | '''1'''\u20130 || rowspan=2 align=center | 4\u20131 || rowspan=2 | [[2019 Africa Cup of Nations qualification]]\n|