G}} || align=center | '''1'''\u20130 || rowspan=2 align=center | 4\u20131 || rowspan=2 | [[2019 Africa Cup of Nations qualification]]\n|-\n| align=center | 10 || align=center | '''3'''\u20130\n|-\n| align=center | 11 || 23 June 2019 || rowspan=2 | [[30 June Stadium]], [[Cairo]], Egypt|| {{fb|KEN}} || align=center | '''2'''\u20130|| align=center | 2\u20130 || rowspan=3 | [[2019 Africa Cup of Nations]]\n|-\n| align=center | 12 || 7 July 2019 || {{fb|GUI}} || align=center | '''2'''\u20130 || style=\"text-align:center\"| 3\u20130\n|-\n| align=center | 13 || 14 July 2019 || [[Cairo International Stadium]], Cairo, Egypt || {{fb|NGA}} || align=center | '''2'''\u20131 || style=\"text-align:center\" | 2\u20131\n|-\n| align=center | 14 || rowspan=2 | 15 October 2019 || rowspan=2 | [[Stade Pierre-Mauroy]], [[Lille]], France || rowspan=2 | {{fb|COL}} || align=center | '''2'''\u20130 || rowspan=2 align=center | 3\u20130 || rowspan=2 | [[Exhibition_game#Association_football|Friendly]]\n|-\n| align=center | 15 || align=center | '''3'''\u20130\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n'''Leicester City'''\n*[[Premier League]]: [[2015\u201316 Premier League|2015\u201316]]<ref name=PremProfile/>\n*[[Football League Championship]]: [[2013\u201314 Football League Championship|2013\u201314]]<ref>{{cite book |editor-first=John |editor-last=Anderson |title=Sky Sports Football Yearbook 2014\u20132015 |year=2014 |publisher=Headline Publishing Group |location=London |isbn=978-1-4722-1251-1 |pages=200\u2013201}}</ref>\n\n'''Manchester City'''\n*Premier League: [[2018\u201319 Premier League|2018\u201319]]<ref name=PremProfile>{{cite web |url=https://www.premierleague.com/players/8983/Riyad-Mahrez/overview |title=Riyad Mahrez: Overview |publisher=Premier League |accessdate=17 May 2019}}</ref>\n*[[FA Cup]]: [[2018\u201319 FA Cup|2018\u201319]]<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/48236232 |title=Manchester City 6\u20130 Watford |first=Phil |last=McNulty |website=BBC Sport |date=18 May 2019 |acces